WEBVTT

00:01:58.703 --> 00:02:00.188
and as a photographer,

00:02:00.212 --> 00:02:02.022
I have the rare opportunity

00:02:02.046 --> 00:02:04.368
to reveal animals and entire ecosystems

00:02:04.392 --> 00:02:07.433
that lie hidden beneath
the ocean's surface.

00:02:07.457 --> 00:02:10.242
You can't love something
and become a champion for it

00:02:10.266 --> 00:02:12.401
if you don't know it exists.

00:02:12.425 --> 00:02:16.647
Uncovering this -- that is the power
of conservation photography.

